ji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解d職員係大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多數係d大陸學生"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"隔離三哥都一齊汁<br />\n可能係商場問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"聽講係譚仔呀姐嚟，咁我又覺得無問題既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴晚食啲態度好好，起碼唔係unun腳拎綜緩班蝗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"其他區嘅加藤屋都係咁？我以為淨係粉嶺先係咁，因為近大陸多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}